Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.17,0:24:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.17,0:24:13.17,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.65,0:24:12.65,Default,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:23:04.77,EDCN,,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.97,0:22:58.73,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那個 我是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.73,0:23:04.02,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}你是溫柔的微笑
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.65,0:23:12.82,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我能想到沒有回答也可以
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.82,0:23:15.20,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}心不在焉的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.20,0:23:20.58,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}那抹幸福的觸感 輕飄飄的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.58,0:23:24.92,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}明天的牽掛 只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.92,0:23:29.84,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}在空中漂浮 轉瞬即逝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.84,0:23:35.68,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}清澈的心知曉愛意
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.68,0:23:39.60,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}不久也會知曉寂寞
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.60,0:23:46.69,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}我們因為道別而緊緊相連
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.69,0:23:51.36,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ah 回到你所等待的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.36,0:23:56.03,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}Ah 回到你所等待的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.03,0:24:00.04,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}相信會有你的一句話
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.04,0:24:04.00,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(0,1000)}歡迎回家
Comment: 0,0:24:12.80,0:24:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,
